End Process

@Reasoning:
Verifies a nested at-rule (@media) containing rule blocks. Exercises
recursive rule parsing because the contained "body { font-size: 14px; }"
must itself be translated through the same code path used at top level.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation:
Increment total. Use the static literal
"@media (max-width: 768px) { body { font-size: 14px; } }".
Translator with 0 options. Branch on hir != 0.
@End Implementation

@TestCases:
- Input @media (max-width: 768px) { ... } -> non-null HIR with nested
  rule, passed += 1
- Parser fails to recurse into the @media body -> failed += 1
- Translator returns 0 on the media-query predicate -> failed += 1
@End TestCases

